    "\tIn order to be capable of fitting a Proton Gun while still maintaining a turret mount, Syndicated Systems had to remove various life support systems, requiring that the pilot wear a pressurized suit rather than having the cabin be fully pressurized. Although it makes piloting a Barb an uncomfortable experience, the result is a level of short-range firepower that is unheard of for a craft its size."
