  {:description
   ["This quite compact radiothermal generator uses isotopes so radioactive, and so tightly packed together, that it could almost be classified as a nuclear reactor."
    "\tAlthough not very impressive in terms of how much energy they produce, Remnant generators have been designed to better handle the energy draining effects of ionization."],
