  {:description
   ["Efficient Remnant technology ensures that nearly all the heat produced by this generator's radioisotopes is converted into electricity instead of becoming waste heat."
    "\tThe Remnant took the ion dissipation effects of the crystals found on Viminal and replicated them for their generators in order to help survive the hostile environment of the Ember Waste."],
