   :cost 2123000}
  {:description
   ["The early Remnant engineers did not trust the finicky and unpredictable nuclear reactors that were then in use in human space, so they instead focused on perfecting the art of radioisotope thermoelectric power."
    "\tThe ion resistance on all Remnant generators not only allows them to bounce back from ion storms more quickly, but also gives their ships a window of time when an ion storm starts where they are not affected, giving them a chance to escape before becoming debilitated by the storm."],
